<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَوْلًا مَّعْرُوفًا}</span> ... قَوْلًا بَعِيدًا عَنِ الرِّيبَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
